tranquil /ˈtræŋkwɪl/

1. ADJ Something that is tranquil is calm and peaceful. 宁静的 

例： The tranquil atmosphere of the inn allows guests to feel totally at home. 这家客栈的宁静氛围让客人们感到宾至如归。 

2. tranquillity N-UNCOUNT 宁静 

例： The hotel is a haven of peace and tranquillity. 这个旅馆是一个宁静的好去处。

